{"tid":1906614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係你呀許生]許智峯公開徵尋電單車撞人群警員身份","createTime":"2020-03-02T05:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T11:15:31.000Z","uid":34409,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d60fb35ef70fc549255471a7f78a71d193cb0c89","tid":1906614,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:10:42.000Z","msg":"【尋人啟示📣｜電單車撞人警員】#追究警暴 #請廣傳 #CommentLikeShare<br />\n<br />\n不能忘記！去年11月11日葵芳三罷行動期間，一名警員駕電單車來回撞去人群，致多名手足倒地受傷，完全是蓄意傷人！早前眾籌承諾私人檢控該名撞人警員，經過與律師團體商討，決定公開徵尋該名警員身份：<br />\n<br />\n許智峯現正呼籲，如有該名警員的資料線索，請即致電 / WhatsApp 9722 6032 聯絡我們，一切資料將會保密！<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳，讓更多人看見，感謝大家！<br />\n<br />\n如想了解有關工作進展，可以追蹤：<br />\nFacebook: 許智峯<br />\nInstagram: huichifung<br />\nYouTube: 許智峯 huichifung <br />\n<br />\n我們不會忘記手足、不會忘記警暴。#五大訴求缺一不可！願公義得到彰顯！<br />\n#公民起訴抗警暴 #第四擊 #尋人啟示 #彰顯公民抗力🔥￼ #毋忘手足 #追究警暴刻不容緩 #港島許智峯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01zi255.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01zi255.jpg&h=04ee8f6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9209fcf6ee996135a534fe9d5462cc3614d23058","tid":1906614,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:11:52.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n我地應該批鬥班激進白票撚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1906610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1906610</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a9cee6d6544c6caba4d7250c3d21fce17f46c461","tid":1906614,"uid":99964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:12:56.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n私人檢控班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a704cdba6964986cc9f8030ed803de8d6f353a7f","tid":1906614,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:16:55.000Z","msg":"好波，大狀黨呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b3d673c5f5482de59b58ef376b4acac4fe3778","tid":1906614,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike"